title: Week 13 preview
itunes:title: Week 13 preview
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- preview the Week 13 games and react to the news of RG III's benching. Plus, the guys play "How well does Chris Wesseling know Katy Perry songs".
